I. Overseas SNS operation Shenzhen
1\.Responsible for overseas social media operation and marketing, including but not limited to the promotion of Twitter/Ins/linkedin/Facebook and other SNS platforms.
2\.Responsible for the maintenance/content operation/activity operation of social media platform homepage, editing attractive social content, planning and organizing marketing activities regularly to increase the number of fans and improve the activity of fans on each platform and expand the company's brand influence.
3\.Localize overseas communication plan for different regions or countries, and cooperate with the team to complete the communication execution.
4\.User research and competitor analysis, familiar with and understand the user situation, and provide multi-dimensional operation plan to initiate user behavior. Job requirements:
1\.Bachelor degree or above, proficient in English listening, reading, writing and translation:
2\.Familiar with SNS platform operation mode, with Facebook, TwitterInstagram marketing experience;
3\.Good at planning various activities, using the fan base to strengthen brand awareness and increase the brand viscosity of users:
4\. Strong copywriting skills, familiar with writing soft copy, event planning copy, with market planning work experience is preferred;
5\. Experience in blockchain industry or have certain knowledge of blockchain is preferred.

Product Director Beijing
Product Director Job Responsibilities:
1、Responsible for the research, planning and actual implementation of trading platform and financial derivatives;
2、Concerned about the business trends of homogeneous products in the industry and digging out the core requirements;
3, collect user and internal feedback, and continue to update and iterate on the product according to the company's business planning:
4, and R & D, testing, operations and other departments to communicate effectively, to ensure their full understanding of the product and promote the product online:
5, monitoring product data, analysis and statistics, continuous improvement of the product, to solve the user pain points; Job requirements:
1、Familiar with the blockchain field or have stock foreign exchange related trading experience;
2、More than 3 years of product management or related work experience
3、Experience in international well-known Internet companies, or product development experience in large Internet platform products
4, with user experience sensitivity, can stand in the user perspective to consider product design ideas:
5、Master the requirement analysis method and process, have the ability to show the product prototype and PRD writing ability;
6、With clear product ideas, the ability to grasp the product as a whole, with strong detail design ability;

C. Finance Director Shanghai/Beijing
I. Job responsibilities:
1、According to the company's strategic planning, develop the financial system of molecular companies and business segment strategic planning and supervise the implementation of the implementation:
2、Assist in the development of the company's business strategy, preside over the development of the Group's financial strategic planning, and is responsible for guiding and supervising its implementation;
3、Responsible for the development of the company's financial system and business segment annual work plan and budget, and ensure the achievement of annual work goals;
4、Responsible for optimizing the company's financial management system, establishing a sound scientific and systematic financial accounting system, financial monitoring system, risk management system, and effective internal control;
5, preside over the development of various financial rules and regulations and work procedures to strengthen risk control, in order to improve the overall financial operation efficiency of the Group;
6, equity financing, major investment projects, mergers and acquisitions and other business activities to provide advice and decision-making support, participate in risk assessment, guidance, tracking and control;
7、Responsible for the construction of the company's financial system and business segment management team and cultivate the financial and professional talents required to meet the company's strategy.
Second, the qualifications:
1, majoring in finance, financial management, with a bachelor degree or above;
2, with more than 5 years of finance-related work experience in medium and large group companies, including more than 3 years of experience in similar or equivalent positions, at least 1 year of experience in the blockchain industry;
3、Experience in successful equity financing, investment, M&A restructuring, etc., able to provide professional advice and suggestions on the reasonable use of corporate funds.
Suggestions;
4、With a comprehensive financial knowledge system, proficient in finance, tax policy, operation analysis, budget management, cost control and cost accounting;
5, with strategic investment, financing and capital management, project negotiations, resource integration, risk control and other comprehensive knowledge and ability;
6、Stable personality, steady, strong risk awareness, excellent strategic thinking and overall awareness.

IV、Overseas Business Distributed
Job duties :
1\.Timely track the development trend of blockchain industry and find global quality projects to cooperate;
2\.Establish cooperation with domestic and foreign projects, formulate cooperation model and expand cooperation channels;
3\.Independently complete project business development, negotiation and project execution;
4\. Keep abreast of the development of blockchain industry, competitor situation, collect market information to help develop project docking strategy
Job Requirements:
1\.Bachelor degree or above, management, marketing, finance, foreign language and other related majors are preferred;
2\.Experience in exchange docking projects is preferred;
3\.English can be used as working language, smooth in listening, reading and writing;
4\.Excellent communication and negotiation skills
5\. Strong BD and sales ability, as well as the ability to develop, communicate, understand, persuade and crisis management;
6\. Strong stress resistance and careful, strong sense of responsibility, like to challenge themselves.

V. Overseas Marketing Director Dubai
Job duties:
1\.Responsible for the marketing development strategy of overseas market, develop annual marketing promotion, brand media PR work plan, realize the company's brand value and marketing concept;
2\.Responsible for market research and analysis, researching the development status of peers and industry, making regular market forecast and intelligence analysis, providing basis for company's decision;
3, responsible for user traffic growth, responsible for organizing and implementing the company's online and offline marketing activities; develop strategic brand communication strategies, enhance the effectiveness and creativity of brand content, as well as continuous exposure:
4, around the brand building and marketing promotion two core objectives, build a complete marketing team, processes, systems and tools, build brand management, digital marketing, content marketing, marketing automation, online and offline integrated marketing system, and introduce innovative solutions from the perspective of market customer experience:Job Requirements:
1, more than 8 years of experience in marketing, more than 2 years of experience in trading platforms, foreign exchange and other related financial industries, with the ability to independently lead
team, with independent planning, implementation of successful cases of brand marketing is preferred:
2, with market acumen, operational planning skills, business negotiation skills and innovation and leadership and coordination skills: 3, strong negotiation and communication skills with customers, with fast learning ability, strong sense of market competition:
4\.Good at cross-departmental organization, communication and coordination of resources, good sense of teamwork.

VI. Overseas Operations Director Dubai
Job Description:
1\.According to the strategic planning and company development, fully coordinate the company operation management, responsible for managing the platform user growth, basic operation, product operation, activity operation, community operation and other modules.
2\.Combine with the current situation of the industry, conduct strategic analysis and research on the platform and the market to improve website traffic, ranking, registration, transaction volume, etc;
3\.Optimize the existing platform operation and management level through the operational data provided by various departments, organize product operation data analysis and market condition analysis, and guide the development and implementation of operation strategies based on the analysis results.
4\.Community and activity operation: Combine the development direction of the platform with the specific operation of internal and external communities, develop and implement operation activity plans and complete data collection and analysis;
5\.Through various operation plans, complete annual, quarterly and monthly user accumulation and growth;
6\. Expand and manage the operation team, establish effective incentive assessment mechanism, ensure the smooth operation of the platform, continuously improve efficiency, guide the team's work and ensure the progress of work development. Job requirements:

1. Fluent in English, best with overseas study background, more than 5 years of internet operation management experience, including more than 2 years of blockchain industry operation management experience:
2. Familiar with the basic process of wallet and exchange operation, operation data analysis; information update and management;
3. Familiar with promotion channels, operation mode, proficient platform, APP and other operation management, with successful blockchain product operation cases

Seven, the domain name product operation director Distributed

1. Responsible for the deep development of domain name industry and related products mining
2. Responsible for conducting market research and analysis, researching peer and industry development, making regular market forecast and intelligence analysis, providing basis for company decision:
   3\.Expand and manage the operation team, establish effective incentive assessment mechanism, ensure the smooth operation of the platform, continuously improve the efficiency, guide the team work situation, ensure the progress of work development Job requirements:
   1\.Bachelor degree or above, aged 30-38, with 5 years or more experience in domain name industry development and related work. Independent team leader, with independent planning, independent operation and development cases is preferred
   2\.With market acumen, operation planning ability, business negotiation ability and innovation ability as well as leadership and coordination ability;
   3\.Good at cross-departmental organization, communication and coordination of resources, good sense of teamwork.

Eight, CTO Shenzhen
Job Description】Job Responsibilities.
1, fully responsible for the technical team formation, echelon construction and all management of the company's technical level.
2, combined with the company's business development needs and the current state of the system, the development of technical development strategy, the system architecture development planning, organization and implementation of major technical decisions and programs.
3、Responsible for the planning, control, supervision and management of the technical solution design, development process, quality and development progress of the whole process from demand to delivery of the product, to ensure the development progress of the company's products, and to conduct quality assessment after completion.
4, the daily operation and maintenance of the platform system, risk audit, risk inspection and risk warning tips and solutions and other related work, and is responsible for system security and stability.
Job requirements.
1、Undergraduate degree or above, majoring in computer or software, with experience in architecture design, proficient in one or more mainstream blockchain system development languages such as go, java, C++, etc.
2、More than five years' experience in blockchain related technology development, more than three years' experience in R&D team management, managing a technical team of not less than 20 people.
3、Familiar with the underlying technology principle of blockchain, familiar with P2P network and distributed storage, familiar with the mainstream consensus mechanism.
4、Familiar with the implementation mechanism and operation principle of ipfs, filecoin, ethereum, openchain, bitcoin, hyperledger and other mainstream blockchain open source projects.
5、Familiar with various data structures and algorithms, research on distributed computing, security protocols, cryptographic algorithms and cloud computing.
6、In-depth understanding of the transaction system, and unique insights into the architecture and mechanism of the transaction system.
7、Strong learning, communication, expression and team management skills.
8、Those who have read the underlying source code and made relevant modifications, or those who have participated in the development of blockchain trading system and contributed source code are preferred.

